ul.li:
Separately as arguments to the following signature of the method: getConnection(String
url, String user, String password)   Connection conn = DriverManager.getConnection(
    "jdbc:derby:myDB", "mary", "little7xylamb");

By setting the user and password properties in a Properties object as
with other connection URL attributes   Properties p = new Properties();
p.put("user", "mary");
p.put("password", "little7xylamb");
Connection conn = DriverManager.getConnection(
    "jdbc:derby:myDB", p);
